HEADWORD: Aërophyte
<hw>A"⟦eum⟧r*o*phyte</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>A⟦eum⟧ro-</ets> + Gr. <grk>fyto`n</grk> plant,
